{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"AI 简历筛选系统 API","description":"基于 Ollama + LangGraph 的智能简历筛选平台","version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/":{"get":{"summary":"Root","description":"API 根路径","operationId":"root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/api/templates":{"get":{"tags":["基础"],"summary":"Get Template","description":"获取评分标准模板\n\n前端可在用户未输入时展示此默认模板","operationId":"get_template_api_templates_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TemplateResponse"}}}}}}},"/api/tasks":{"post":{"tags":["任务管理"],"summary":"Create Task","description":"创建招聘任务\n\n1. 提交岗位需求\n2. 返回 task_id 用于后续上传简历","operationId":"create_task_api_tasks_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CreateTaskRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TaskResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/tasks/{task_id}/upload":{"post":{"tags":["任务管理"],"summary":"Upload Resumes","description":"上传简历文件\n\n- **task_id**: 创建任务后返回的 ID\n- **files**: 多份 .docx 简历文件（最多 20 份）\n\n上传后后端开始异步处理，前端需轮询任务状态","operationId":"upload_resumes_api_tasks__task_id__upload_post","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"multipart/form-data":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/Body_upload_resumes_api_tasks__task_id__upload_post"}}}},"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/tasks/{task_id}":{"get":{"tags":["任务管理"],"summary":"Get Task Status","description":"查询任务状态\n\n前端轮询此接口获取处理进度（建议 3 秒/次）\n\n状态说明：\n- **pending**: 等待上传简历\n- **processing**: 处理中（stage: extracting/evaluating/ranking）\n- **completed**: 处理完成\n- **failed**: 处理失败","operationId":"get_task_status_api_tasks__task_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TaskResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}},"delete":{"tags":["任务管理"],"summary":"Delete Task","description":"删除任务及文件","operationId":"delete_task_api_tasks__task_id__delete","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/tasks/{task_id}/result":{"get":{"tags":["结果查询"],"summary":"Get Task Result","description":"获取任务结果\n\n仅在状态为 completed 时可调用，返回：\n- Top 3 候选人详细信息\n- 所有候选人排名列表\n- 分数分布统计（用于 Dashboard）","operationId":"get_task_result_api_tasks__task_id__result_get","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TaskResultResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/api/tasks/{task_id}/dashboard":{"get":{"tags":["结果查询"],"summary":"Get Dashboard Data","description":"获取 Dashboard 图表数据\n\n专为前端图表组件设计的数据格式：\n- **score_distribution**: 分数分布（柱状图）\n- **skill_radar**: Top 3 技能对比（雷达图）\n- **level_pie**: 熟练度占比（饼图）","operationId":"get_dashboard_data_api_tasks__task_id__dashboard_get","parameters":[{"name":"task_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","title":"Task Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DashboardData"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"Body_upload_resumes_api_tasks__task_id__upload_post":{"properties":{"files":{"items":{"type":"string","contentMediaType":"application/octet-stream"},"type":"array","title":"Files"}},"type":"object","required":["files"],"title":"Body_upload_resumes_api_tasks__task_id__upload_post"},"CandidateProfile":{"properties":{"name":{"type":"string","title":"Name","description":"姓名"},"relevant_years":{"type":"integer","title":"Relevant Years","description":"相关经验年限"},"education":{"additionalProperties":{"type":"string"},"type":"object","title":"Education","description":"教育背景","example":{"degree":"本科","school":"XX 大学"}},"skill_matrix":{"items":{"additionalProperties":true,"type":"object"},"type":"array","title":"Skill Matrix","description":"技能矩阵"},"expected_salary":{"type":"string","title":"Expected Salary","description":"期望薪资","example":"30-40K/月"}},"type":"object","required":["name","relevant_years","education","skill_matrix","expected_salary"],"title":"CandidateProfile"},"CandidateResult":{"properties":{"filename":{"type":"string","title":"Filename","description":"简历文件名"},"profile":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/CandidateProfile","description":"候选人画像"},"evaluation":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EvaluationResult","description":"评估结果"}},"type":"object","required":["filename","profile","evaluation"],"title":"CandidateResult"},"CreateTaskRequest":{"properties":{"job_description":{"type":"string","title":"Job Description","description":"岗位需求描述","example":"高级 Python 后端工程师，5 年以上经验.